{"tid":2296464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國宣布：派 航 母 部 署 到「遠東地區」","createTime":"2020-11-22T13:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T04:40:02.000Z","uid":227801,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b96a5ec1cdd2bde87619e3e7f083965b6a52506b","tid":2296464,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201122/JFNYY5KMABA3DNXFOIZO3H7J6I/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0F61CMNABtieIVI8yR2pUPxthBTG66iXQxEGmw9sq8gS-VZRLlRpV09TI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201122%2FJFNYY5KMABA3DNXFOIZO3H7J6I%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0F61CMNABtieIVI8yR2pUPxthBTG66iXQxEGmw9sq8gS-VZRLlRpV09TI&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItTwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=c32ba6e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201122%2FJFNYY5KMABA3DNXFOIZO3H7J6I%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0F61CMNABtieIVI8yR2pUPxthBTG66iXQxEGmw9sq8gS-VZRLlRpV09TI&h=e5a3d279\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201122/JFNYY5KMABA3DNXFOIZO3H7J6I/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0F61CMNABtieIVI8yR2pUPxthBTG66iXQxEGmw9sq8gS-VZRLlRpV09TI</a><br />\n英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）日前宣佈，2021年將把航空母艦派往亞洲，相關軍事計劃還包括設立太空與網路部隊。因為香港問題，英國與中國關係出現緊張，外界預料英方此舉或激怒中國。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜日前透過視像對國會發言指出：「伊利莎白女王號（HMS Queen Elizabeth）航空母艦明年將率領英國與盟邦組成的特遣艦隊，執行我們20年來規模最大的部署任務，範圍涵蓋地中海、印度洋及東亞。」<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜未進一步透露詳細部署計劃，但英國《泰晤士報》（The Times）7月曾報道，英國國防大臣已擬定一項計劃，要將伊利莎白女王號部署到遠東地區。這艘航艦可能會參與美國和日本的聯合演習，以及阻止海洋主權過度聲索的自由航行作業。<br />\n<br />\n《日經亞洲》（Nikkei Asia）網站指出，英國其他官員也曾提出對亞太地區派遣航艦的可能性，不過現在是約翰遜首度證實此一構想。《日經亞洲》分析，英國此舉可能是為了向中國傳達一項訊息。中國因對香港日益打壓，而導致與英國外交關係緊張。<br />\n<br />\n除了出動航艦外，約翰遜也宣佈，成立國家網路部隊（National Cyber Force）和「太空司令部」（Space Command），以因應新興國安威脅。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"e6349edc758fac63818e943475eead2628b34213","tid":2296464,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"Trump有可能不成功, 重跟機？"},{"pid":"69742bceeaf9712bb46584c0c5b5db09640adec9","tid":2296464,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:28:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54ad6ee19d6aa3bfb40066022f9a834618fc402c","tid":2296464,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"劍指台灣"},{"pid":"6e6c91f793482cca6e86cc775bad0e3c2bab38e6","tid":2296464,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71ecbfc9f18c1549a80a35591959f484a15ca907","tid":2296464,"uid":179729,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e6349edc758fac63818e943475eead2628b34213","tid":2296464,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"Trump有可能不成功, 重跟機？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"反共係全球共識，奶共都偽"},{"pid":"4655781f756cbcc4bd931b8d6f107aba0e86c70c","tid":2296464,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ecbfc9f18c1549a80a35591959f484a15ca907","tid":2296464,"uid":179729,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e6349edc758fac63818e943475eead2628b34213","tid":2296464,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"Trump有可能不成功, 重跟機？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"反共係全球共識，奶共都偽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"<del>偽</del> 係"},{"pid":"c0774c11dbd70f869582583123cd6818e1db999c","tid":2296464,"uid":146934,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime